trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 데이터를 제공는 <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted"> </xref> 이벤트입니다.

trans-unit.source: Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName> event to receive notification when the new document finishes loading.
trans-unit.target: 처리는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>새 문서 로딩이 완료 될 때 알림을 받을 수는 이벤트입니다.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs object passed to the event handler lets you retrieve the location of the new document through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs 개체를 통해 새 문서 위치를 검색할 이벤트 처리기 수에 전달 되는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A>속성.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs.Url%2A>

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName> event occurs, the new document is fully loaded, which means you can access its contents through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>이벤트가 발생 하면 새 문서는 완전히 로드 즉, 해당 내용을 통해 액세스할 수 있습니다는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, 또는 <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName>속성.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentCompleted?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserDocumentCompletedEventArgs"></xref> class.
A <xref:System.Uri> representing the location of the document that was loaded.
Gets the location of the document to which the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser"></xref> control has navigated.
